---
title: Easy Sweet-Soy Ginger Pork Poke Bowl with Cheat's Sushi Rice & Sriracha Mayo
description: Poke bowls are a favourite for something quick, fresh and delicious, but there’s no need to order a takeaway when it’s so easy to throw together at home! Add flavourful and fragrant pork, crunchy fresh veggies and charred corn to a bowl of zingy-sweet sushi rice for a taste explosion that’ll have you questioning why you ever ordered out at all.
This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.
